name: Pear Tree and Partridges
description:
This hand tinted print of ‘Pear Tree and Partridges’ forms part of Amanda’s series of ’British Trees and Native Wild Animals’.
Limited Edition Print of just 50. Printed on fine quality Saunders Waterford HP watercolor paper.
All the green pears are hand painted, making each picture unique and collectable. The print is signed and numbered. 

Comes in a white mount that fits a standard square frame size.

Posted 1st class Recorded Royal Mail within UK. Same price postage for up to 3 prints. 

Paper size:  21cm x 21cm
Image size: 15cm x15cm
Mount size: 23cm x 23cm
